## Rules

1. Never use arbitrary colors or fonts — always use the brand palette above.
2. Use CSS custom properties (`--color-primary`, `--color-secondary`, etc.) instead of hardcoded hex values.
3. Include the company logo in headers, title slides, and document footers.
4. For the complete design system with CSS variables, slide templates, and usage guidelines, refer to `skills/company-design-system/SKILL.md`.
